            "description": "Returns WebSocket server metrics:\n- Server status: running (normal operation), stopping (graceful shutdown), error/crashed (failed unexpectedly)\n- Active connections: current number of connected clients (synced from game server in real-time)\n- Total connections: cumulative connections since server start\n- Bytes sent/received: network traffic metrics\n- Uptime: time server has been running in seconds\n- Last error: if any, shows error message and timestamp\n\nThresholds and Alerts:\n- Active connections = 0 with status running: server ready, awaiting connections\n- Active connections > 500: monitor performance\n- Active connections > 900: warning condition\n- Status = error/crashed: critical alert, immediate investigation needed\n- Status = stopping: maintenance mode, no new connections accepted"
